{
  "stem": "18637.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had a bad feeling for those who were bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like those-- this-- those five bad people, who used to go at night, and do whatever they want, Misiura found a way to persuade them, they should come in to his-- to his place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he worked-- worked with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know if he got them this way, or he got them the other way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he-- he brought three, the two brothers and the police-- the kommandant, the-- the-- they were higher than they were from--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yuk's brothers, the two, Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yuk brothers, the two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one was-- I don't remember his name, but he was the kommandant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- when-- when the Germans was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, yeah, you will go with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm going-- you'll work with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He brought them before the-- before the place where they were, before the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said like that, he-- to Purim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and to him, he said, it's enough to kill innocent people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's enough to rape Jewish girls, kill them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Purim and Alek, I think-- I wasn't there-- killed those three, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he-- they took revenge of those three people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were more but on those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One ran away to Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because a lot of them ran away with the-- with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a couple of years ago, they called from Australia if-- what happened?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If I knew Ivanechko?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I says, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We used to be afraid for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We used to hide from him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to kill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know what? 30 Christian people came to Australia to give evidence that they saw how they killed this and this, the woman and child, and by name.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
